title: Survivor Micronesia - Season 16 - Complete

Survivor: Micronesia - Fans vs. Favorites was the sixteenth season of the CBS reality television series Survivor. Pitting die-hard Survivor fans against some of the series&#039; past contestants, this season was the show&#039;s third to include contestants from past seasons, after the all-returning contestant pool from Survivor: All-Stars and Survivor: Guatemala in which two contestants from Survivor: Palau returned for a second chance.
